# For a FLAT CLONE of this pipeline (scripts at the repo root): the working root is this
# directory, so setup.sh and the stages create their output folders right here. Keep them
# out of git. In the thesis layout the root is the PARENT and these live one level up,
# covered by the thesis-root .gitignore, so the entries below then match nothing and are inert.
# NB: .gitignore has no inline comments — a trailing "# ..." becomes part of the pattern.

